sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Store
    participant DroPilot System
    participant Supplier
    participant PaymentGateway
    participant AI Engine

    User->>Store: Register/Login
    Store->>DroPilot System: Authenticate User
    DroPilot System->>User: Confirm Authentication
    User->>Store: Create/Customize Store
    Store->>DroPilot System: Store Setup Request
    DroPilot System->>AI Engine: Generate Store Content
    AI Engine->>DroPilot System: Return Generated Content
    DroPilot System->>Store: Apply Store Settings
    User->>Store: Manage Products
    Store->>DroPilot System: Product Management Request
    DroPilot System->>Supplier: Fetch Product Data
    Supplier->>DroPilot System: Return Product Data
    DroPilot System->>AI Engine: Enhance Product Descriptions
    AI Engine->>DroPilot System: Return Enhanced Descriptions
    DroPilot System->>Store: Update Product Listings
    User->>Store: Place Order
    Store->>DroPilot System: Process Order
    DroPilot System->>PaymentGateway: Validate Payment
    PaymentGateway->>DroPilot System: Confirm Payment
    DroPilot System->>Supplier: Forward Order
    Supplier->>DroPilot System: Confirm Order Receipt
    DroPilot System->>Store: Update Order Status
    Store->>User: Send Order Confirmation
    User->>Store: Request Analytics
    Store->>DroPilot System: Generate Reports
    DroPilot System->>Store: Provide Analytics Data
    Store->>User: Display Reports